HEADWORD: Unweave
<hw>Un*weave"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>weave</ets>.]</ety> <def>To unfold; to undo; to
